abstract: Air France flight attendants plan to strike Oct. 29 to Nov. 2.
snippet: Air France flight attendants plan to strike Oct. 29 to Nov. 2.
lead_paragraph: Air France flight attendants plan to strike from Oct. 29 to Nov. 2. In a statement released on Thursday the airline said it expected 80 percent of its flights to operate on Oct. 29. For the other dates, capacity has yet to be determined.

headline.main: Air France Flight Attendants to Strike
